Title: Inverse Compliance Score Weighting
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2018-05-16
Author: Peter M. Aronow <peter.aronow@yale.edu>, Dean Eckles
        <icsw@deaneckles.com> and Kyle Peyton <kyle.peyton@yale.edu>
